source: Add a new visibility option based on roles
target: Eine neue Sichtbarkeitsoption hinzufügen, die auf den Rollen basiert

source: If enabled, Content Managers will not be able to see or edit content that has visibility enabled for that role.
target: Wenn diese Option aktiviert ist, können Content Manager keine Inhalte sehen oder bearbeiten, für die Sichtbarkeit für diese Rolle aktiviert ist.

source: Show this role as a visibility option
The @name doesn't have enough permissions to see the group content.
The group visibility is set to @role, the user @name doesn't have this role.
Third party settings for role visibility
target: Einstellungen von Drittanbietern für die Sichtbarkeit von Rollen

source: This option lets you hide this role’s profile details from people with different roles. People with the same role will still be able to interact with each other’s profile details.
You can not delete this role because you have follow entities with this visibility (see above)
You can not uncheck this box because you have follow entities with this visibility (see above)
only visible to members with the assigned role(s)
